193    public function buildArticle(Article $article, array $overrides = []): self
194    {
195        // The story id of the article (if it's a wire, we need to add the agency and the feed name)
196        $articleStoryId = '';
197        // Check article type
198        if ($article->isWire()) {
199            // Modifiers : modify page programs : It has to be 'wires' for wire articles. Even if apollo send something else
200            $program = new Program(['id' => AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_NAME_WIRE]);
201            $article->setProgram($program);
202            // If the article is a wire, we want to add more information, such as the agency key and the wirefeed key
203            $articleStoryId .= $article->getAgencyKey().'|'.$article->getWireFeedKey().'|';
204        } elseif ($article->isNoComment()) {
205            // Modifiers : modify page vertical & theme : It has to be 'news' for nocomment. Even if apollo send something else
206            $article->setVertical(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_NAME_NEWS);
207            if (!empty($article->getMainTheme())) {
208                $article->getMainTheme()->setUrlSafeValue(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_NAME_NEWS);
209            }
210        }
211
212        $this->buildVideo($article);
213
214        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageVertical($this->getAdobeVertical($article));
215        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageTheme($this->getAdobeTheme($article));
216        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageProgram($this->getAdobeProgram($article));
217        // Article eventid -> id
218        if (!empty($article->getId())) {
219            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleEventId((string) $article->getId());
220        }
221        // Article storyid -> cid
222        if (!empty($article->getCid())) {
223            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleStoryId($articleStoryId.$article->getCid());
224        }
225        $pageName = $this->adobeAnalyticsPageNameBuilder->buildArticle($article);
226
227        // Article title
228        if (!empty($article->getTitle())) {
229            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleTitle(mb_strtolower($article->getTitle(), 'UTF-8'));
230        }
231        // Article updatedate
232        if (!empty($article->getLastPublishedDate())) {
233            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleUpdateDate($article->getLastPublishedDate()->format('d/m/Y'));
234        }
235        // Article nbDaysSincePublication
236        if (!empty($article->getPublishedAt())) {
237            $nbDay = round((time() - $article->getPublishedAt()) / 86400);
238            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleNbDaysSincePublication($nbDay); // from seconds to days
239        }
240        // Article format
241        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleFormat(AdobeAnalytics::ARTICLE_FORMAT_STANDARD);
242        // Article type
243        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleAdvertisingType($article->getAdvertisingType());
244        // Article hasVuukle
245        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleHasVuukle($article->hasVuukle());
246        // page name
247        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageName($pageName);
248        // Set pagetype
249        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPagePageType(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_TYPE_ARTICLE);
250        // Set page contentType
251        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageContentType(AdobeAnalytics::CONTENT_TYPE_TXT);
252        // Set Article author
253        $author = $article->getMainAuthor();
254        if ($author) {
255            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleAuthor($author->getTitle());
256        }
257
258        if (!is_null($article->getProgram()->getTitle())) {
259            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleProgram($article->getProgram()->getTitle());
260        }
261
262        $concatenatedTitleTags = $article->getConcatenatedTitleTags();
263        if ($concatenatedTitleTags) {
264            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleTags($concatenatedTitleTags);
265        }
266
267        if ($article->hasTechnicalTags()) {
268            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleTechnicalTags(implode(',', $article->getTechnicalTags()));
269        }
270
271        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setDisplayBreakingNewsbar($article->isAdobeFromBreakingNews());
272
273        if ($article->isNoComment()) {
274            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageProgram(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_NAME_NOCOMMENT);
275        }
276        if ($article->isBulletin()
277         || $article->isNoComment()) {
278            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageContentType(AdobeAnalytics::CONTENT_TYPE_STREAM);
279            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPagePageType(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_TYPE_VOD);
280            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleFormat(AdobeAnalytics::ARTICLE_FORMAT_VIDEO);
281        }
282
283        $this->applyOverrides($overrides);
284
285        return $this;
286    }

288    private function applyOverrides(array $overrides): void
289    {
290        foreach (array_keys($overrides) as $key) {
291            if (!in_array($key, AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEYS)) {
292                throw new \InvalidArgumentException(sprintf('Invalid override key "%s"', $key));
293            }
294        }

296        if (isset($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_CONTENT_TYPE])) {
297            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageContentType($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_CONTENT_TYPE]);
298        }
299
300        if (isset($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_URL])) {
301            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPagePageUrl($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_URL]);
302            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setUrlPath($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_URL]);
303        }
304
305        if (isset($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_NAME])) {
306            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageName($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_NAME]);
307        }
308
309        if (isset($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_TYPE])) {
310            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPagePageType($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_PAGE_TYPE]);
311        }
312
313        if (isset($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_ARTICLE_FORMAT])) {
314            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setArticleFormat($overrides[AdobeAnalytics::OVERRIDE_KEY_ARTICLE_FORMAT]);
315        }
316    }
317
318    private function buildVideo(Article $article): self
319    {
320        if (!$article->hasVideo()) {
321            return $this;
322        }
323
324        $player = match ($this->articlePlayer->getPlayerType($article)) {
325            Player::IFRAME_TYPE => AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_PLAYER_IFRAME_NAME,
326            Player::DAILYMOTION_TYPE => AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_PLAYER_DM_NAME,
327            Player::PFP_TYPE => AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_PLAYER_PFP_NAME,
328            Player::JW_TYPE => AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_PLAYER_NAME,
329            default => AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_PLAYER_ERROR,
330        };
331
332        // Set video player name
333        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoPlayerName($player);
334        // Set video type
335        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoType(AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_TYPE_VOD);
336
337        // Set video duration
338        if (!empty($article->getMainVideo()) && $article->getMainVideo()->getDuration() > 0) {
339            $duration = $article->getMainVideo()->getDuration() / 1000;
340            if (!is_int($duration)) {
341                $duration = (string) $duration;
342            }
343            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoDuration($duration);
344        }
345        // Set video dailymotionId
346        if (!empty($article->getDailymotionId())) {
347            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoDailymotionVideoId($article->getDailymotionId());
348        }
349        // Set video youtubeId
350        if (!empty($article->getYoutubeId())) {
351            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoYoutubeVideoid($article->getYoutubeId());
352        }
353        // Set video house number
354        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoHouseNumberVidid($article->getHouseNumber());
355
356        if (isset($article->getVersions()['en']['url'])) { // try to get the english version if exist
357            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoName($article->getVersions()['en']['url']);
358        } elseif (!empty($article->getUrl())) {
359            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoName($article->getUrl());
360        }
361
362        if (!empty($article->getPublishedDate())) {
363            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoPublicationDate($article->getPublishedDate()->format('d/m/Y'));
364        }
365
366        if (!empty($article->getId())) {
367            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoVideoId((string) $article->getId());
368        }
369
370        // Set pagetype
371        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPagePageType(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_TYPE_ARTICLE);
372        // Set page contentType
373        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageContentType(AdobeAnalytics::CONTENT_TYPE_STREAM);
374
375        return $this;
376    }

594    /**
595     * Bulletin page builder
596     *
597     * @param array $articleVideos of video articles
598     */
599    public function buildVideoBulletin(array $articleVideos): self
600    {
601        if (isset($articleVideos[0])) {
602            $this->buildArticle($articleVideos[0]);
603        }
604        $housenumber = [];
605        $duration = [];
606        $name = [];
607        $playerName = AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_PLAYER_NAME;
608        // Loop on video articles to generate a housenumber chain separated by '|'
609        /** @var Article $article */
610        foreach ($articleVideos as $article) {
611            // Check if article contain a video
612            if ($article->hasInternalVideo()) {
613                $playerName = $this->articlePlayer->getPlayerType($article) ?? AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_PLAYER_NAME;
614                $housenumber[] = $article->getHouseNumber();
615                $duration[] = $article->getMainVideo()?->getDuration() / 1000;
616                if ($article->getUrl() && $article->getUrl() !== '') {
617                    $name[] = $article->getUrl();
618                }
619            } else {
620                $housenumber[] = 'na';
621                $duration[] = 'na';
622                $name[] = 'na';
623            }
624        }
625        // Set housenumbers
626        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoHouseNumberVidid(implode('|', $housenumber));
627        // Set durations
628        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoDuration(implode('|', $duration));
629        // Set name
630        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoName(implode('|', $name));
631        // Set video is in playlist
632        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoIsinplaylist(true);
633        $pageName = $this->adobeAnalyticsPageNameBuilder->buildVideoBulletin();
634        // Set page name
635        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageName($pageName);
636        // Set pagetype
637        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPagePageType(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_TYPE_VOD);
638        // Set pageVertical
639        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageVertical(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_NAME_NA);
640        // Set pageTheme
641        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageTheme(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_NAME_MULTI);
642        // Set pageProgram
643        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageProgram(AdobeAnalytics::PAGE_NAME_MULTI);
644        // Set page contentType
645        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageContentType(AdobeAnalytics::CONTENT_TYPE_STREAM);
646        // Set video player name
647        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoPlayerName($playerName);
648        // Set video type
649        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setVideoType(AdobeAnalytics::VIDEO_TYPE_VOD);
650
651        return $this;
652    }

1012    public function generateNewArticleDataLayer(Article $article, ?Request $request = null): string
1013    {
1014        // Reset dataLayer.
1015        $this->initDataLayer();
1016
1017        // Build the video build also the article ;)
1018        $this->buildArticle($article);
1019
1020        // Articles must to have the content type equals to `txt`
1021        $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPageContentType(AdobeAnalytics::CONTENT_TYPE_TXT);
1022
1023        // Rewrite URL with right path (and not url from the request)
1024        if (!empty($request)) {
1025            $pageUrl = sprintf('%s%s', $request->getHttpHost(), $article->getPath());
1026            $parameters = $request->getQueryString();
1027            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setPagePageUrl($pageUrl.(!empty($parameters) ? '?'.$parameters : ''));
1028            $this->adobeAnalyticsDataLayer->setUrlPath(strtok($pageUrl, '?'));
1029        }
1030
1031        return $this->generateDataLayer();
1032    }
